      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like no matter what i do it gets worse. i try to ignore it but then a new post or a joke about me pops up and it's just like... i'm constantly on edge. it feels like the whole world is just watching me fail and laughing. i'm so tired of feeling like this. it's like this constant weight in my chest and i just want it to stop. i just want everything to be quiet for once.",
